reviews.review_text: Pre-FM Reels Interesting how the crowd sound isn't so apparent as in Schnucke reels. Which makes me wonder if that's fake. I'm grateful for all the streams that are surfacing and even w/ background line hiss it is separate from all music. These '76 shows have such a delicate fine quality that still amazes me.
best stella blue ever one of the best stella blues ive heard in the 20+ years that i have been listening to the Grateful Dead!
